{"tid":1659822,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人嚟，開戰線！11月9號係World Freedom Day!!!!","createTime":"2019-10-17T07:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T11:16:10.000Z","uid":3513,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ea4a6e2b1a190ca92460fbc6af0702fcec8b7558","tid":1659822,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"11.1 11.2 有家樂牌巴搞緊blizzcon既野 準備weconnect遠在美國既手足 聲援聰哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱俾我google 到 11月9號就係World Freedom Day<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紀念柏林圍牆終於倒下 共產黨喺東歐既極權瓦解手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抗共 反抗 </span></span>咩？<br />\n我地唱榮光<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 唔係祈求民主與自由咩？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足！ 做野呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbc534129c265ea1a067647dac96e5a94a2e572","tid":1659822,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:12:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0cbdfcf87e3c9fe1e123329d067ba005fa5b1b10","tid":1659822,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"941bc41eca6e6e78de2a025463ce4b8674294827","tid":1659822,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:12:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2633442fa7e40d2fd9a5b4a346a2183a37551c64","tid":1659822,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:13:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e21640cebd9a16f310651a95dd4b16617c7a0723","tid":16