/a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x7a20U0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx7a20U0.png&h=9d15fd04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/slasher/status/1184545687784038401?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fslasher%2Fstatus%2F1184545687784038401%3Fs%3D21&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=49c462b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fslasher%2Fstatus%2F1184545687784038401%3Fs%3D21&h=16fcf882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/slasher/status/1184545687784038401?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n外國人都係咁支持我地，<br />\n被共雪罰停賽！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地唔係唔幫拖煲大佢呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同一時間<br />\ndreamwork都奶共！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nDior都話台灣係屬於中國！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\ntwitter team已經將所有<br />\nDreamwork Dior Blizzard Tweets<br />\n放哂入Bot 仲會不斷更新！<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgBvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=41b13e59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n<br />\n今次男女老幼咩人都關事！<br />\n快啲同美國講，<br />\n中共響唔同界別控制緊所有公司，<br />\n控制全世界的思想！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">入  /task2</span></span><br />\n就可以見到哂啲tweets<br />\nretweet and cm please!<br />\n要煲大中共用緊跨國公司控制緊男女老少的思想，進行大一統洗腦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nWswUhd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnWswUhd.png&h=737683c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"178acbfecc4559bad18b03d38715eea3ce3f2c6a","tid":1659822,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"